projects.name: CreativePOP
projects.description: Founded during the COVID-19 lockdown, CreativePOP is the first online volunteer-based tutoring platform focused on creative subjects for primary school students (grades 1 - 6) in Indonesia.

projects.name: Twitter Scraper
projects.description: A Python program that scrapes Tweets related to certain search terms and visualises the data as a word cloud. Developed using the Twitter API and various Python libraries (nltk, numpy).

projects.name: Office Hours Queue
projects.description: A queue for office hours with different user permission levels and functionalities depending on access need. Made using Bootstrap and jQuery for the front end, and MySQL and PHP to for the back end.
